 */

/**
 * @defgroup policy Policy
 * @brief Decoder/encoder/RTSP/memory policy decision helpers used by the builder.
 */

/**
 * @defgroup internal_sima Framework internals (SiMa reach-through)
 * @brief Reach-through layer between core/ and the SiMa SoC pipeline internals.
